promoterAddress: Block No. 42, Taxshila Society, Behind Dargah, Timbavadi, Junagadh Junagadh 362001

formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
Payment receipt for construction permission from local authority is attached along with Commencement certificate.
Payment of Taxes, cess, fees, charges, premiums, interest etc. to any Statutory Authority includes Rs.24,240 paid to Junagadh Municipal Corporation for sub-plotting.					
Promoter further estimates to incur Rs. 1,63,880 towards obtaining RERA registration and quarterly return legal fees.					
Thus Payment of taxes, cess, fees etc estimate is Rs. 1,88,120 while incurred and paid is Rs. 24,240.
LAND COST
As per Gujarat RERA Circular dated 5th Oct, 2018 vide Circular No. 11/ 2018, we have been allowed to take Indexed cost of acquisition or ASR whichever is higher as fair market value of land. In pursuance of same, we have taken ASR value as the fair market value of land in our calculation of land cost. Total Land area - 16,188 sq.mtr. X Rs. 545/ sq.mtr. (Jantri value of stamp as per supritendent of stamps, Gandhinagar Gujarat) = Rs. 88,22,460. Detailed land cost calculation with jantri value is attached in Form 1 NOC tab.
